sequenceDiagram

    participant U as User
    participant M as MAUI App
    participant A as ASP.NET API
    participant Q as Redis Streams
    participant E as Embedding Worker
    participant B as BGE-M3
    participant P as PostgreSQL

    U->>M: Create note

    M->>A: Save note

    A->>P: Insert note

    A->>Q: Publish note_created

    Q->>E: Consume event

    E->>B: Generate embedding

    B-->>E: Vector

    E->>P: Insert embedding

    E->>P: Insert context_ledger entry